The '''Alderaanian gunship''' was a type of military vessel manufactured or operated by [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]].

==History==
Ships of this type were donated to the [[Alliance Fleet/Legends|Rebel Alliance Fleet]] prior to the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]]. They participated in that battle.

